[920 E Burnside St, Portland, OR 97214](https://maps.app.goo.gl/6YfeNt9V6m9YDDAd7) (11 min walk)  
‚ÄúYour bar / restaurant / plant paradise / neighborhood escape inside the Jupiter NEXT Hotel.‚Äù Chill and relaxing vibes, but also with events like the Dolly Parton Birthday Bash and regular ‚ÄúFemmes & Thems‚Äù happy hours and day parties with R\&B and jazz DJs.

